ZH_CN: 有些军队在空中，有些则地面。
ZH_TW: 有些軍隊在空中，有些則地面。

EN_US: Please don't try to command your infantry to attack an aircraft.
ES_ES: Please don't try to command your infantry to attack an aircraft.
ZH_CN: 请不要尝试命令步兵攻击飞机。
ZH_TW: 請不要嘗試命令步兵攻擊飛機。

EN_US: Equipment can give your army a better performance on the battle.
ES_ES: Equipment can give your army a better performance on the battle.
ZH_CN: 装备可以使您的军队在战斗中有更好的表现。
ZH_TW: 裝備可以使您的軍隊在戰鬥中有更好的表現。

EN_US: Mages have a special attack method: There will be a bonus splash attack within 1 cell.
ES_ES: Mages have a special attack method: There will be a bonus splash attack within 1 cell.
ZH_CN: 法师有一种特殊的攻击方法：1个格内的所有敌方会受到一个额外的溅射攻击。
ZH_TW: 法師有一種特殊的攻擊方法：1個格內的所有敵方會受到一個額外的濺射攻擊。

EN_US: Riflemen attack every enemy in a line.
ES_ES: Riflemen attack every enemy in a line.
ZH_CN: 火枪手可以攻击在一条线上的所有敌人。
ZH_TW: 火槍手可以攻擊在一條線上的所有敵人。

EN_US: Aircraft Fighters have to go back to its airport at the end of the turn.
ES_ES: Aircraft Fighters have to go back to its airport at the end of the turn.
ZH_CN: 战斗机必须在回合结束时返回机场。
ZH_TW: 戰鬥機必須在回合結束時返回機場。

EN_US: Airships can sent more aircraft fighter.
ES_ES: Airships can sent more aircraft fighter.
ZH_CN: 飞艇可以派遣更多的战斗机。
ZH_TW: 飛艇可以派遣更多的戰鬥機。
